{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>《Light HDR》是一款將你的 iPhone 或 iPad 轉變為專業級燈光面板的強大應用程式，今天限時免費中，它專為攝影師、錄影師以及所有追求完美光線的創意工作者而設計。這款應用能有效解決行動裝置在拍攝時光線不足或色彩不準的問題，讓你在任何場景下都能精準控制光源，捕捉到最完美的影像，絕對是行動創作的理想選擇。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/460x460bb-75-107.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>精準色彩調控</h2>\n    <p>《Light HDR》充分釋放裝置 XDR 顯示器潛力，帶來極致亮度與真實 HDR 光效。使用者可透過白平衡、RGB、HSV 模式，精準調控光線色彩輸出，確保影像色準。藉由 Metal 優化技術，提供流暢即時 HDR 渲染體驗，讓專業級行動燈光控制更加便利。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1290x2796bb-80-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1290x2796bb-81-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1290x2796bb-82-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1290x2796bb-83-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1320x2868bb-79-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/2064x2752bb-11-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：Light HDR</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Photo &amp; Video</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T22:07:14.277544+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":344,"images":7,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}